{"tid":670683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法羅群島獨立運動　人口是澳門十分一（5萬人）　獨立大熱","createTime":"2018-05-19T14:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T11:38:29.000Z","uid":47714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0a8a28a90a7c31f3a6d12d74ce5c89f009dac2","tid":670683,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.storm.mg/article/350905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F350905&d=U71G0TWnB5URXsXGsVz6tZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5bfe9181\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.storm.mg/article/350905</a><br />\n<br />\n[image]<a href=\"https://goo.gl/d4WNxo[/image]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fd4WNxo%5B%2Fimage%5D&d=U71G0TWnB5URXsXGsVz6tZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=fa02703e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/d4WNxo[/image]</a><br />\n<br />\n位於距離丹麥本土900公里的北邊島嶼，屬於該國的海外自治領地，因地處偏僻形成了自有的文化及傳統，島上居民僅5萬多人，儘管該島曾在1946年發起獨立公投，最後卻無疾而終仍隸屬於丹麥管轄，但法羅群島獨立運動一直都是島上的熱門話題，目前該島分成勢均力敵的獨立派及統一派。"},{"pid":"95c85c72a3431ab7e426169ce4762b1fa9bc1a66","tid":670683,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.storm.mg/article/350905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F350905&d=U71G0TWnB5URXsXGsVz6tZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5bfe9181\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.storm.mg/article/350905</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/d4WNxo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fd4WNxo&h=cfe8dc98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位於距離丹麥本土900公里的北邊島嶼，屬於該國的海外自治領地，因地處偏僻形成了自有的文化及傳統，島上居民僅5萬多人，儘管該島曾在1946年發起獨立公投，最後卻無疾而終仍隸屬於丹麥管轄，但法羅群島獨立運動一直都是島上的熱門話題，目前該島分成勢均力敵的獨立派及統一派。"},{"pid":"05410190002e96768e00b882dd423c2fcb16ba6d","tid":670683,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"h